!! ## Font settings
!Xft.dpi:        96
!Xft.antialias:  true
!Xft.rgba:       rgb
!Xft.hinting:    true
!Xft.hinstyle:   full
!
!! === fusion color scheme ===
!! special
!*foreground:   #c5c8c6
